==English==
===Etymology===
[[Arabic]] [[{{ARchar|'''فندق'''}}]]   ''fun'duq''

===Pronunciation===
*funduuk or fonduq
===Noun===
'''fonduk'''
# a [[North]] [[African]] or an [[Arabian]] [[inn]] or [[hotel]]. Fonduk basically means a [[hotel]] in [[Arabic]] but in standard Arabic it means an [[inn]] or a [[manor house]]. The word entered the [[English]] [[dictionary]] during the 19th and 20th centuries.
